<div class="container py-3">
    <h2 class="py-3">We offer pay as you go for every ads</h2>
    <p>Hectic work is now over. All you have to do is wait and see how your business grow with medialk.com. We give you the most simplest and the fastest way to monitor your advertisements. Our advertisement support in three languages (English, Sinhala & Tamil). You can now archive your audience through different cultures.</p>
    <h3 class="py-3">What you have to do</h3>

    <h4><strong>Choose your objective</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">To choose the right ad objective, answer the question "what's the most important outcome you want from this ad?" - It could be sales on your website, download links to your apps or increased brand awareness.</p>

    <h4><strong>Pick a format</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">Which audience you want? (English, Sinhala or Tamil you have to select) Pick an age format. Your targeted audience age criteria (ex-21 years to 45 years)</p>

    <h4><strong>Pick an Audience location</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">In which region you want to run your add (ex-In Gampaha District)</p>

    <h4><strong>Set your budget</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">Enter your daily or lifetime budget, and the time period which you want your ads to run. (Eg-03 days or 7 days) These limits mean that you'll never spend more than you're comfortable with.</p>

    <h3 class="py-3">What you have to do</h3>

    <h4><strong>Select your audience</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">Based on your requirements, we choose your audience – such as age, location and other details – choose the demographics, interests and behaviors that represent your audience at its best.</p>

    <h4><strong>Decide where to run your ad</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">Next, We select where your advertisement want to run. Based on your goals we select right audience.</p>

    <h4><strong>Measure and manage your ad</strong></h4>
    <p class="py-2">When your ad is running, you can track performance and edit your campaign by contacting us. See if one version of your ad is working better than another, or if your ad is being delivered efficiently, and make tweaks and adjustments as needed.</p>

    <div class="pb-3 h4">
        For more details Contact us (<a href="@Url.Action("Contact","Home")">click here</a>)
    </div>
</div>

